+# Wave 6 Plan (20260302w6a)
+
+## Scope (in)
+1. Implement PM4 ingestion cron/hash-ledger flow (scan, hash-dedupe, persisted ledger, summary artifact).
+2. Add ingest endpoint client wiring (`/ingest_content`) and CLI runner (`ingest:bonfires`).
+3. Remove hard-coded personal agent-name assumptions from config/spec/docs/tests to support general multi-user adoption.
+
+## Non-goals (out)
+1. No changes to retrieval/capture business logic semantics.
+2. No live scheduler daemon beyond plugin timer hook + CLI run-once command.
+
+## Acceptance criteria
+1. Ingestion run computes hashes and ingests only new/changed content; unchanged content is skipped.
+2. Ledger persistence prevents duplicate re-ingest after restart.
+3. Summary artifact records scanned/ingested/skipped/errors.
+4. Plugin/docs/specs no longer require specific personal agent names.
+5. `npm run gate:all` passes.
